A.P.V.N.Sarma
Full Name: Avva Padmanabha Venkata Narayana Sarma (easier to write / address as A.P.V.N.Sarma!)
Was Collector and District Magistrate in Nalgonda, Guntur and Warangal districts of Andhra Pradesh.
Was Member Secretary Andhra Pradesh State Electricity Board.
Was Secretary to Government of Andhra Pradesh in General Administration (Political) Department and in Health, Medical and Family Welfare Departments in A.P.
Was Chairman and Managing Director, Singareni Collieries Company Limited.
Was Joint Secretary, Ministry of Coal, Government of India.
Was Executive Officer, Tirumala Tirupati Devasthanams.
Was Special Chief Secretary, Department of Social Welfare, Government of A.P.
Was Secretary to Government of India, Ministry of Shipping and retired in that job on 31st October, 2009.
